results.title: Watch and eye dock - iPhone 6 slim
results.description:
The Watch and Eye dock is minimalistic and a feature rich solution to both charge and display your Iphone 6. This Dock\/valet has an integrated slot that can keep 3 to 4 watches at the ready. A carved pocket in the base can store eyeglasses, sunglasses, or other items you may carry in your daily life. A slot to the side can securely store a wallet or check book. Additional storage can be found in the rear of the dock for keys or change etc. You release your dock from the valet with a simple push of a finger through the slot at the top. This slot also allows for you Iphone 6 to lay completely flat and secure in the dock with room for the camera lens. The dock's lean back on its shelf is perfect for facetime. I left just a little room around the phone in case you use a candy shell or thin gel style case. \
\
\
The details: \
\
Curved wire path allows the phone and wire to be removed without disrupting the dock\/valet. \
\
Slot provided for 3 to 4 watches, depending on size\
\
Front pocket can store eyeglasses, sunglasses, pens etc.\
\
Rear storage pockets can store keys, pocket change, ear-buds, and plenty of other items you may choose to carry in your pockets. \
\
Item ships USPS priority 1 to 3 day mail\
\
This is meant to be used with an iphone 6 without a case or a very thin case. For larger case options please see our other listings.\
\
This docking station has been sanded smooth and finished with boiled linseed oil.\
\
Aprx. 7 inches tall x 10 inches wide with a food print of 4 x 10 inches.  \
\
Made out of Oak plywood in the USA by Chris Fandz\
\
PLEASE NOTE: On hand stock quantities will vary. If this is for a gift and should ship out before 2 weeks after purchase, please send me a convo.
